## Choosing between options
When weighing technical options, choose on **correctness, scalability, and
maintainability first — discount build effort.** The fastest-to-type option is
often the low-quality one; you can build the better design in minutes, so pick the
one you'd want to live with, not the one that's cheapest to write.
